ðŸ”¬This is a nightly-only experimental API. (`io_slice_advance`Â [#62726](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/62726))

Advance the internal cursor of the slice.

Also see [`IoSliceMut::advance_slices`](about:blank/struct.IoSliceMut.html#method.advance_slices "associated function std::io::IoSliceMut::advance_slices") to advance the cursors of multiple buffers.

##### [Â§](#panics-1)Panics

Panics when trying to advance beyond the end of the slice.

##### [Â§](#examples)Examples

```
#![feature(io_slice_advance)]

use std::io::IoSliceMut;
use std::ops::Deref;

let mut data = [1; 8];
let mut buf = IoSliceMut::new(&mut data);

// Mark 3 bytes as read.
buf.advance(3);
assert_eq!(buf.deref(), [1; 5].as_ref());
```

